text: Ðis syndon ða landgemere ðere V hida æt Eblesburnan.
Of ðam welige on ðone witan weg.
Of ðam wege on ðone hassuc upp an hrofan hricge.
Of hrofan hricge on Dolemannes beorh.
Of ðam beorge on ða greatan dic.
Of ðam beorge on ðæt hlew et hrichwege.
Of hrichwegge on ða witan dic.
Of ðam hlince on ðæt seade clif.
Of ðere burnan on ða streat.
Ðis is ðara V hyda boc æt Eblesburnan ðe æðelræd cyning gebocodæ ælfgare his þegne on ecæ yrfe.
